                {"q": "What is confirmation bias?", "a": "The brain's natural tendency to seek information that confirms existing beliefs and dismiss contradicting information."},
                {"q": "What does developing critical thinking require?", "a": "Practice and intellectual humility — the willingness to admit you might be wrong, seek challenging viewpoints, and change your mind when evidence demands it."}
